        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "But the rest of us rather looked with favour on the Story Girl's idea. We felt sure that she would do penance as picturesquely and thoroughly as she did everything else.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
