        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "\"I've thought of a great penance,\" said Cecily eagerly.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "\"Don't go to the missionary meeting to night.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "The Story Girl looked piteous.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "\"I thought of that myself-but I CAN'T stay home, Cecily.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000041_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000041_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "I MUST hear that missionary speak.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000041_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000041_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "No, I must go, but I'll tell you what I'll do.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000041_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000041_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "I'll wear my school dress and hat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000041_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000041_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "THAT will be penance.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000041_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000041_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "I hate it so.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000041_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000041_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "It's such dreadful tasting stuff-but it's a good blood purifier, so Aunt Janet can't object to it.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000042_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000042_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "All day she sat in the kitchen and worked buttonholes, subsisting on bread and water and Mexican Tea.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000043_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000043_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "The smell of raisin pies is something to tempt an anchorite; and the Story Girl was exceedingly fond of them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000043_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000043_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "Felicity ate two in her very presence, and then brought the rest out to us in the orchard.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000043_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000043_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "But she worked on at her buttonholes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000043_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000043_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "Pat came over, but his most seductive purrs won no notice from his mistress, who refused herself the pleasure of even patting him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000044_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000044_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "The Story Girl slipped over home, and when she came back we gasped.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000046_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000046_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "I want to mortify the flesh-\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000047_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000047_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "Go right home and dress yourself decently-or eat your supper in the kitchen.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000049_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000049_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "And she had tied her hair with a snuff brown ribbon which was very unbecoming to her.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "The first person we saw in the church porch was mrs Ray.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000053_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000053_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "\"Oh, I don't know.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000053_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000053_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "I feel better since I punished myself.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000053_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000053_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "But I'm going to make up for it to morrow,\" said the Story Girl energetically.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000053_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000053_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "\"In fact, I'll begin to night.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000053_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000053_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "Wasn't the missionary splendid?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000053_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000053_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "That cannibal story was simply grand.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "\"I'd like to be a missionary and have adventures like that,\" said Felix.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000059_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000059_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "Two cents more a week out of Cecily's egg money, meant something of a sacrifice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000059_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000059_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "It inspired the rest of us.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000060_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000060_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "I won't be able to give much.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000060_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000060_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "But I'll do the best I can.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000060_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000060_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "Are there any Methodist heathen?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000060_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000060_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "I s'pose I ought to give my box to them, rather than to Presbyterian heathen.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000061_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000061_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
        "content": "\"No, it's only after they're converted that they're anything in particular,\" said Felicity.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-451_126826_000061_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/451/126826/451_126826_000061_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-451",
